name: Setlist
body:
# Documentation

Documentation is currently being maintained on our internal JQI wiki; however, we will post a PDF dump whenever anything major is changed. If you have questions, feel free to email or submit an issue.

The "root" page from the wiki documentation is actually called "New SetList", and is located on pg. 16 of the pdf (see table of contents).

[SetList Documentation](docs/SetListDocumentation.pdf)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
